title: demonsaw_windows
description: DemonSaw is a secure and anonymous file sharing application that makes security simple and gives you back control of your data. DemonSaw provides you with a way to create your own network or join a public DemonSaw network so that you can share and communicate securely. DemonSaw was created to free us from the oppression of governments and corporations who are committed to destroying our privacy. They have no right to our secrets and it's time we do something to take back control. http://glodls.to/uploads/images/26032790.jpg http://glodls.to/uploads/images/26032791.jpg
